            <li styleclass="Body Text HowTo" style="margin-top:0px; margin-bottom:0px;">As you add a new sketch-element (<text styleclass="Element">Line</text>, <text styleclass="Element">Arc</text>, <text styleclass="Element">Blend-Curve</text>), hover above a <text styleclass="Element">Point</text> at the end of an existing sketch-element, then drag to add the new sketch-element.</li>
